io.wcm.qa.glnm.selectors.base

Interface Selector

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    NestedSelector
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractNestedSelectorBase, AbstractSelectorBase, FixedValueNestedSelector, FixedValueSelector, SelectorCorrectionsWrapper, SelectorFromLocator, SelectorFromString

    public interface Selector
    Interface to represent selectors in Galenium. Selectors are used to identify elements in a page. This interface is used throughout Galenium up to the final hand off to Galen (as Locator) or Selenium (as By).
    Since:
    1.0.0
